{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban all unpaid work trials",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government ban unpaid work trials to ensure that people cannot be legally exploited for free labour.",
        "background": "I want the Government to make it clear in law that businesses cannot have people on unpaid work trials, and that anyone in a work trial must be paid. Currently, companies are able to trial people, and have them work all day for free, and then not employ them or even contact back.",
